title: Let's Watch TV: Ru Paul's Drag Race
description:
Joe finally gets a chance for payback! Just as Fran made him watch her favorite show the Bachelor, Joe returns the favor and they watch Ru Paul's drag race. Fran starts a new glossary of drag terms and they play a fun game of "finish the sentence" to close out the episode.
